<span class="dim">                        |</span>
<span class="dim">            +-----------v-----------+</span>
<span class="dim">            |</span>       <span class="hl">Worker</span>           <span class="dim">|</span>     <span class="dim">Bare metal, /dev/kvm</span>
<span class="dim">            |</span>                       <span class="dim">|</span>
<span class="dim">            |</span>  <span class="dim">+---vm-1-----------+</span>  <span class="dim">|</span>
<span class="dim">            |  |</span> <span class="hl">Firecracker VM</span>    <span class="dim">|  |</span>     <span class="dim">Zero secrets</span>
<span class="dim">            |  |</span> Agent + workload  <span class="dim">|  |</span>     <span class="dim">Ephemeral, disposable</span>
<span class="dim">            |  |</span>   <span class="dim">|</span>               <span class="dim">|  |</span>
<span class="dim">            |  +---|---------------+  |</span>
<span class="dim">            |      |                   |</span>
<span class="dim">            |  +---v---------------+  |</span>
<span class="dim">            |  |</span> <span class="hl">TLS Proxy</span>         <span class="dim">|  |</span>     <span class="dim">Injects credentials</span>
<span class="dim">            |  |</span> Per-VM, ephemeral <span class="dim">|  |</span>     <span class="dim">at the network layer</span>
<span class="dim">            |  +-------------------+  |</span>
<span class="dim">            +-----------------------+</span></pre>
